1. Danas sam obavio *kupovinu* u marketu. (Today, I did some *shopping* at the market.)
2. Nisam siguran da li ću uspeti da platim *kupovinu* ovog meseca. (I'm not sure if I'll be able to pay for my *shopping* this month.)
3. Ukoliko želite da izbegnete gužvu, savetujem vam da odete na *kupovinu* ranije. (If you want to avoid the crowd, I suggest you go *shopping* earlier.)
4. *Kupovina* putem interneta je sve popularnija u današnje vreme. (Online *shopping* is becoming increasingly popular these days.)
5. Ovo je prvi put da sam u ovoj prodavnici i već sam pronašao sve što mi treba za *kupovinu*. (This is my first time in this store, and I've already found everything I need for my *shopping*.)
6. Zašto si kupio toliko namirnica? Zar ne misliš da si pretjerao sa *kupovinom*? (Why did you buy so much groceries? Don't you think you went overboard with your *shopping*?)
7. Prošle nedelje sam obavio *kupovinu* garderobe za celu porodicu. (Last week, I did some *clothes shopping* for the whole family.)
8. Moram da idem na *kupovinu* pre nego što zatvori prodavnica. (I need to go *shopping* before the store closes.)